<br />I've made a Galaxian cart before, it was a simple one. I'm not scared off by some wire jobs. I've fitted large eproms to smaller sockets before.
<br />
<br />I got a program called tnines and it seems to be doing the job well of spliting up the rom into pgm and chr (as well has the hdr but that doesn't matter).
<br />
<br />I "was" making a california raisins on a pro wrestling pcb but my desoldering iron tip is just about worn out and it made a couple real nasty cuts on some traces of the pcb that where not worth repairing.
<br />
<br /> If anoyne has pics of a finished FF2 that would be great as I'm a very tactile learner and images really help me wrap my head around things.

		

