	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As long as it's a short famicom cart, it should fit in a nes cart (which both ff2 &amp; ff3 are). If you don't care about fitting the game in a cart (and are using a toploader), any game that uses standard controllers will work.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


