		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">sevast wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">...stackup...</div>
<br />
<br />Pretty much any cartridge around that time will do it, but I've seen a stack up with a basic NROM board.
<br />
<br />If you want a definite NES-JOINT board and adapter, make sure to go to a used game shop and look for the heaviest one you can find. I have a Hogans Alley cart with the joint board because of this.

		

		</td>
